<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>詩詞 on Script Adults</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/categories/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/</link><description>Recent content in 詩詞 on Script Adults</description><image><title>Script Adults</title><url>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/images/papermod-cover.png</url><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/images/papermod-cover.png</link></image><generator>Hugo -- 0.128.2</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 22:33:12 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://katsuragicsl.github.io/categories/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>無題</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%84%A1%E9%A1%8C/</link><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 22:33:12 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%84%A1%E9%A1%8C/</guid><description>陳衣欲搗子規啼，嗽穿重簾夜更淒。
十載茅齋茂陵臥，雙行枯淚太常妻。
清心昔捨青雲路，俗務今催洗耳溪。
半世徒勞芳自賞，來生捨筆執鋤犁。</description></item><item><title>憶遊摩周湖</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%86%B6%E9%81%8A%E6%91%A9%E5%91%A8%E6%B9%96/</link><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2026 02:31:54 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%86%B6%E9%81%8A%E6%91%A9%E5%91%A8%E6%B9%96/</guid><description>久慕摩周泊，霙遊弟子町。
盤湖青壁峭，漫靄雪濱暝。
水闊連雲影，藍深莫片萍。
天鵝神渚過，幾欲問仙齡。</description></item><item><title>漫郎愁</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%BC%AB%E9%83%8E%E6%84%81/</link><pubDate>Sat, 25 Apr 2026 19:24:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%BC%AB%E9%83%8E%E6%84%81/</guid><description>平生福禍求諸己，豈冀張良借箸籌。
怨得春時秋亦去，芳時不待漫郎愁。</description></item><item><title>拗相公</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%8B%97%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%AC/</link><pubDate>Sat, 25 Apr 2026 19:23:19 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%8B%97%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%AC/</guid><description>煩言少語漠修飾，鐵石心腸拗相公。
滿腹嗔痴熬鬱結，唯題恚賦怨長空。</description></item><item><title>春病</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%98%A5%E7%97%85/</link><pubDate>Sat, 25 Apr 2026 19:22:34 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%98%A5%E7%97%85/</guid><description>春衫濕濕雨還淹，爽颯何知昨日炎。
一暖一寒多感冒，鉛頭鉛瞼鐵毫尖。</description></item><item><title>宿酒</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%AE%BF%E9%85%92/</link><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 18:12:05 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%AE%BF%E9%85%92/</guid><description>乃耳春桃赤，方乾竟欲斟。
酣歌忘篋笥，宿酒爛柯尋。</description></item><item><title>直鉤詞</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%9B%B4%E9%89%A4%E8%A9%9E/</link><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 18:10:42 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%9B%B4%E9%89%A4%E8%A9%9E/</guid><description>嘗聞我氏姜牙祖，百煉參來妙直鉤。
際遇諒如垂澗釣，樵漁宿志待成周。</description></item><item><title>望金鐘雨</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%9C%9B%E9%87%91%E9%90%98%E9%9B%A8/</link><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 18:07:27 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%9C%9B%E9%87%91%E9%90%98%E9%9B%A8/</guid><description>眺望金鐘雨，禁思海外朋。
聞琴忘荈冷，曲散熄孤燈。</description></item><item><title>白梣詠</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%99%BD%E6%A2%A3%E8%A9%A0/</link><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 16:13:59 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%99%BD%E6%A2%A3%E8%A9%A0/</guid><description>郊車瞥白梣，逸氣惹馳心。
獨直杆齊宇，無憂眾鑠金。
貧泥生色潔，倔質抵風侵。
且倚柴亭樹，朱門少此陰。</description></item><item><title>苦戀樹</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%8B%A6%E6%88%80%E6%A8%B9/</link><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 16:02:32 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%8B%A6%E6%88%80%E6%A8%B9/</guid><description>苦楝鄉音訛苦戀，人皆笑我若情痴。
情皆巧合亦如此，插柳方成連理枝。</description></item><item><title>煙塵望</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%85%99%E5%A1%B5%E6%9C%9B/</link><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 16:00:04 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%85%99%E5%A1%B5%E6%9C%9B/</guid><description>稻謝樓空鳥失巢，矛平戟鏽馬生郊。
髫兒道側尋劬母，怕見霜綾掛樹梢。</description></item><item><title>理箱見舊稿</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%90%86%E7%AE%B1%E8%A6%8B%E8%88%8A%E7%A8%BF/</link><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 15:58:51 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%90%86%E7%AE%B1%E8%A6%8B%E8%88%8A%E7%A8%BF/</guid><description>嘗來翻舊札，拙作惡難評。
弱歲初經事，繁文欲釣名。
浮詞堆綺句，躁筆抹虛情。
老喜栽詩卉，閒窗細剪莖。</description></item><item><title>晚詠</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%99%9A%E8%A9%A0/</link><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 15:57:39 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%99%9A%E8%A9%A0/</guid><description>山連千樹翠，暉映半川紅。
日暮同歌賦，杯乾意未窮。</description></item><item><title>茗汁詞</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%8C%97%E6%B1%81%E8%A9%9E/</link><pubDate>Sat, 18 Apr 2026 02:45:06 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%8C%97%E6%B1%81%E8%A9%9E/</guid><description>學淺無他藝，唯長雕琢詞。
沉吟常入定，點卯每來遲。
久病多清興，離群出詭思。
方酣濡墨盡，茗汁代塗之。</description></item><item><title>宦海</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%AE%A6%E6%B5%B7/</link><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 22:06:01 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%AE%A6%E6%B5%B7/</guid><description>棲身宦海辭難直，隱沒丹心色自萎。
若學嵇公棱角出，便難割肉細君遺。</description></item><item><title>閏怨</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E9%96%A8%E6%80%A8/</link><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 22:04:35 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E9%96%A8%E6%80%A8/</guid><description>涼風捲髮斷多少，深館籠眉鎖幾重。
縱有沉魚驚世色，夫征不復枉芳容。</description></item><item><title>詠志</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%A9%A0%E5%BF%97/</link><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 22:02:31 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%A9%A0%E5%BF%97/</guid><description>生似離弦箭，宜將鵠志求。
才情師子建，韜略效留侯。
過隧應斬岸，逾河當折舟。
無教箭虛落，白髮泣春秋。</description></item><item><title>李恥杜愁</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%9D%8E%E6%81%A5%E6%9D%9C%E6%84%81/</link><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 22:01:14 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%9D%8E%E6%81%A5%E6%9D%9C%E6%84%81/</guid><description>性俗全無墨在胸，冥搜拙句砌機峰。
詩成引得謫仙恥，筆落愁催工部容。
既與深情詩韻繫，何教秉賦櫟樗庸。
如吾堪作違心事，簡朽帛殘枯筆封。</description></item><item><title>野火</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E9%87%8E%E7%81%AB/</link><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 21:57:38 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E9%87%8E%E7%81%AB/</guid><description>野火吹焦來撲鼻，疑斯處亦啟兵端。
蒼天果有好生德，怎使狼煙剪不完。</description></item><item><title>稱病歸沐其二</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%A8%B1%E7%97%85%E6%AD%B8%E6%B2%90%E5%85%B6%E4%BA%8C/</link><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 02:23:01 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%A8%B1%E7%97%85%E6%AD%B8%E6%B2%90%E5%85%B6%E4%BA%8C/</guid><description>欲借銀鉤掛輕絅，披襟快意抱江潮。
紅塵每每多煩事，擲笏臥花看九霄。</description></item><item><title>灣仔商廈觀圬者</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%95%86%E5%BB%88%E8%A7%80%E5%9C%AC%E8%80%85/</link><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 02:22:35 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%95%86%E5%BB%88%E8%A7%80%E5%9C%AC%E8%80%85/</guid><description>久困雕欄內，而無玉砌求。 無乾圬者汗，盡濕富人樓。 貴族連三代，貧門到白頭。 笙歌聽愈擾，喋喋不安休。</description></item><item><title>遙寄故人</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E9%81%99%E5%AF%84%E6%95%85%E4%BA%BA/</link><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 02:20:58 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E9%81%99%E5%AF%84%E6%95%85%E4%BA%BA/</guid><description>昨問他鄉花幾許，君稱今日滿山紅。
東風知汝遙憶我，一片吹來孤座中。</description></item><item><title>稱病歸沐登獅子山</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%A8%B1%E7%97%85%E6%AD%B8%E6%B2%90%E7%99%BB%E7%8D%85%E5%AD%90%E5%B1%B1/</link><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 02:18:58 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%A8%B1%E7%97%85%E6%AD%B8%E6%B2%90%E7%99%BB%E7%8D%85%E5%AD%90%E5%B1%B1/</guid><description>甫陟蒼巔氣清朗，忽憂仕路暗傷神。
何時始得閒如許，莫待衰顏惹滓塵。</description></item><item><title>夜讀</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%A4%9C%E8%AE%80/</link><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 02:16:13 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%A4%9C%E8%AE%80/</guid><description>無意尋春色，離群獨筆耕。
風幽星火動，葉蕩夜蟲鳴。
案上半尋闊，心田萬畝宏。
思潮如碧海，引棹到三更。</description></item><item><title>不寐</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E4%B8%8D%E5%AF%90/</link><pubDate>Thu, 09 Apr 2026 02:21:55 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E4%B8%8D%E5%AF%90/</guid><description>夜起喉酸胸似火，窗前恍惚浴寒暉。
素娥招我隨風去，忘卻愁思入繡闈。</description></item><item><title>敢擬一詩忖度離鄉客家人愁緒</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%95%A2%E6%93%AC%E4%B8%80%E8%A9%A9%E5%BF%96%E5%BA%A6%E9%9B%A2%E9%84%89%E5%AE%A2%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA%E6%84%81%E7%B7%92/</link><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 16:11:13 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%95%A2%E6%93%AC%E4%B8%80%E8%A9%A9%E5%BF%96%E5%BA%A6%E9%9B%A2%E9%84%89%E5%AE%A2%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA%E6%84%81%E7%B7%92/</guid><description>久滯繁華地，鄉離語更乖。
夢中歸故里，簷下一聲𠊎。</description></item><item><title>書癖</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%9B%B8%E7%99%96/</link><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 01:11:11 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%9B%B8%E7%99%96/</guid><description>鼯埋松果鴃懸屍，陋室徒藏百冊詩。 開卷恐污長不讀，秦皇應笑我愚痴。</description></item><item><title>葵涌工廈會友</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%91%B5%E6%B6%8C%E5%B7%A5%E5%BB%88%E6%9C%83%E5%8F%8B/</link><pubDate>Sun, 05 Apr 2026 19:09:57 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%91%B5%E6%B6%8C%E5%B7%A5%E5%BB%88%E6%9C%83%E5%8F%8B/</guid><description>取徑葵涌道，良朋相飲來。
人閒車馬靜，路黦綠苔開。
風送天雲遠，霞留暮色哀。
頹垣將拆盡，客別舊樓臺。</description></item><item><title>悼從祖祖父</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%82%BC%E5%BE%9E%E7%A5%96%E7%A5%96%E7%88%B6/</link><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 21:57:29 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%82%BC%E5%BE%9E%E7%A5%96%E7%A5%96%E7%88%B6/</guid><description>清明未至立新冢，香火盈堂幡引魂。
冒雨梨花開遍野，迎風淚眼念先恩。</description></item><item><title>冀嶺南景色依舊</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%86%80%E5%B6%BA%E5%8D%97%E6%99%AF%E8%89%B2%E4%BE%9D%E8%88%8A/</link><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 01:58:05 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%86%80%E5%B6%BA%E5%8D%97%E6%99%AF%E8%89%B2%E4%BE%9D%E8%88%8A/</guid><description>樹倚東籬側，清池阡陌間。
萬田如一色，青嶂繞千鬟。
胡寇鐵馬盛，唐家薪火頑。
